Co. started process of splitting
business as required by amended Insurance Act 2011, Elias Edu,
corporation secretary of Kampala-based co., says by e-mail,
without providing further details.  * All insurance cos. are required to separate insurance
businesses by Sept. 2014  *  NOTE: National Insurance Corp. is unit of Lagos,
Nigeria-based Industrial & General Insurance Plc, which bought
